model.name: Furr2005 - whole-body vitamin A metabolism in humans

notes.p: "Stable isotope dilution techniques for assessing vitamin A status and bioefficacy of provitamin A carotenoids in humans" by Harold and his Furry friends (2005)
The original model was coded in WinSAAM. There the delay compartment was modelled as a series of connected pseudo-compartments. We use the same approach here.
